findChildNodes

public java.util.List findChildNodes(CrNodeVersion parentNodeVersion)
Get all child nodes for a node/version. The child/parent relationship set is lazy loaded to make things more efficient. But as the repository doesn't keep the session open, the lazy loading can't occur! So load manually.
